OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FJust 16% of children in Cardiff can
OL,7,Fswim, according to data collected by
OL,8,FCardiff Metropolitan University and
OL,9,FSwim Wales.
OL,11,FBut Cardiff council says it's coming
OL,12,Fup with a plan to make sure as many
OL,13,Fchildren as possible get the chance to
OL,14,Flearn to swim in school.
OL,16,FAccording to the data, only 57% of
OL,17,Fprimary schools in the city sent
OL,18,Fpupils to swimming lessons in 2022 to
OL,19,F2023.
