OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FA teacher from Ysgol Nant Caerau says
OL,7,Fthe cost of living crisis could be the
OL,8,Freason why fewer children know how to
OL,9,Fswim.
OL,11,F"For me, it's such an important thing.
OL,12,FSwimming is a life skill to have
OL,13,Fespecially for children and younger
OL,14,Fchildren these days," she said.
OL,16,F"It's so important for them to develop
OL,17,Fthe basic skills for swimming. I know
OL,18,Fthat children in my class really have
OL,19,Ffound swimming lessons positive in the
OL,20,Fpast two weeks and they can't wait to
OL,21,Fcarry on the swimming lessons."
