OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FWhen asked why she thought fewer
OL,7,Fchildren know how to swim, Ms Bird
OL,8,Fsaid: "If I'm completely honest then I
OL,9,Fdo think it's the cost of living
OL,10,Fcrisis.
OL,12,F"Swimming lessons are so expensive and
OL,13,Fwe are lucky enough to have the school
OL,14,Fpay for the two weeks' lessons for the
OL,15,Fchildren to be able to have the
OL,16,Fswimming lessons."
