OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FAdham Mahmood, a swimming instructor
OL,7,Fat Western Leisure Centre, said: "By
OL,8,Fbeing at the leisure centre, they
OL,9,Flearn how to get inside the pool
OL,10,Fsafely, what should they be looking
OL,11,Faround for - like safety signs - and
OL,12,Fto understand the area around them.
OL,14,F"So, they learn the safety of
OL,15,Fswimming, as you don't have to be a
OL,16,Fswimmer but you have to be safe in
OL,17,Fwater."
OL,19,FScrutiny committee member, Cllr
OL,20,FCatriona Brown-Reckless, said she was
OL,21,Fshocked by these new figures.
