OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,F"I was really saddened. I'm a mother
OL,7,Fand my children get to swim and I want
OL,8,Fto see other children get to learning
OL,9,Fhow to swim," she said.
OL,11,F"We have a lot of swimming pools in
OL,12,FCardiff - there isn't really a
OL,13,Fshortage of facilities - but what I do
OL,14,Fsee is when I come to swimming pools
OL,15,Fduring term time during school days,
OL,16,Fthey are often relatively quiet. We've
OL,17,Fgot these facilities, so let's use
OL,18,Fthem."
