OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FLevels of swimming ability are
OL,7,Fassessed against the Nofio Ysgol
OL,8,FSchool Swimming and Water Safety
OL,9,Fstandard.
OL,11,FHannah Guise, Swim Wales National
OL,12,FLearn to Swim manager, said that
OL,13,Fswimming lessons are getting expensive.
OL,15,F"The average cost for swimming lesson
OL,16,Fin Wales is #7.66 for a 30 minute
OL,17,Flesson, which is actually a 21 percent
OL,18,Fincrease since 2020," she said.
