OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,F"So, it's beyond the means for a lot
OL,7,Fof people in our community to afford
OL,8,Fto pay for swimming lessons. So, they
OL,9,Fare reliant on schools taking their
OL,10,Fchildren to give them lessons for
OL,11,Fthese potentially life saving skills."
OL,13,FCardiff's figures are significantly
OL,14,Flower than the Welsh average, which is
OL,15,F41%.
