OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FGLL, which runs leisure centres in
OL,7,FCardiff, is currently coordinating
OL,8,Fwith a number of other swimming
OL,9,Fproviders to work out how to improve
OL,10,Fschool swimming and boost use during
OL,11,Fquieter periods.
OL,13,FData collated by GLL shows membership
OL,14,Fhas increased across its leisure
OL,15,Fcentres between March 2023 and March
OL,16,F2024. However, numbers are down at a
OL,17,Fnumber of locations compared with 2019
OL,18,Ffigures.
