OL,3,CWhy nearly 8 in 10 children in Cardiff
OL,4,Ccan't swim
OL,6,FMaindy Centre has seen the biggest dip
OL,7,Fsince 2019 with 820 fewer members,
OL,8,Ffollowed by Llanishen Leisure Centre
OL,9,Fwith a drop of 545 members.
OL,11,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Swimming should be one of the range
OL,13,Fof physical activities that learners
OL,14,Fparticipate in as part of the new
OL,15,FCurriculum for Wales.
